text: Long before Meghan Markle became the Duchess of Sussex, she was an actress and activist, the star of Suits and a United Nations women's advocate for gender equality and women's empowerment. Meghan spent several years in the spotlight before joining the royal family, attending hundreds of events and making appearances all over the world. Here, a look back at Meghan Markle's pre-royal evolution.
